Usage: set_sense [-help] <pin_or_port_list> [-clocks <clock_list>] {[-positive | -negative | -stop_propagation ] [-type <type_list> ]}

-help                  # Prints out the command usage
<pin_or_port_list>     # List or collection of pins or ports (string, required)
-clocks <clock_list>   # List of clocks passing through the specified objects
                       # to which the constraint applies (string, optional)
-negative              # Positive phase filtered clocks pass through the
                       # specified objects (bool, optional)
-positive              # Negative phase filtered clocks pass through the
                       # specified objects (bool, optional)
-stop_propagation      # Stops the propagation of specified clocks and clock
                       # source data paths passing through the specified
                       # objects (bool, optional)
-type <type_list>      # Applies clock sense to object types specified in
                       # type_list: {all | clock | clock_source_data | data}
                       # (string, optional)